<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7399098>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Ventral structures of Aneflomorpha crypta Lingafelter, n. sp., A. minuta Chemsak, and A. rectilinea Casey. a) A. crypta, head and prothorax. b) A. crypta, partially cleared mesosternum. c) A. minuta, head and prothorax. d) A. minuta, partially cleared mesosternum. e) A. rectilinea, partially cleared mesosternum." ;
